  "key_mechanics": [
    "Elevator shaft has 4 levels: room 6 (bottom), room 9 (level 2), room 11 (level 3), room 14 (top). GO SHAFT enters from adjacent rooms.",
    "Duct maze (rooms 25-33) is confusing. The path to the basement is: room 7→GO DUCT→room 25→D→29→D→32→D→33→D→34 (basement).",
    "FEEL direction (FEEL NORTH, FEEL SOUTH, etc.) in the floating sky (room 18) reveals hidden offices with gems (rooms 21, 23).",
    "Chemical Lab (room 13): MIX WEB needs torn paper (formula) + exotic chemicals. MIX acid + calcium carbonate for another reaction.",
    "Room 39 has all three chemicals: Acid, Calcium Carbonate, Exotic chemicals. Take them to lab (room 13).",
    "Penthouse (room 15) has thermostat. SET THERMOSTAT stops the fan in the duct, allowing safe passage.",
    "Computer room (room 17): TYPE commands on keyboard. RUN QUEST, LIST, DIR, CAT NEWS for clues.",
    "LOOK NICHE in elevator shaft level 4 (room 14) finds hidden items.",
    "OPEN DESK in Tony's office (room 2) to find torn paper with web fluid formula.",
    "Treasure room is room 37 (Madame Web's office). DROP all gems there for points.",
    "Villains: Lizard (room 4), Ringmaster (room 3), Doctor Octopus (room 34), Electro (room 34), Hydroman (room 38).",
    "SHOOT WEB at villains after making web fluid in the lab.",
    "Limbo (room 40) is the death room. DOWN returns to Tony's office (room 2)."
  ],
